<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>Your business insurance is now up for renewal with Kingsbridge.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Have you considered enhancing your cover with one of our policy add-ons?</span></p><div><span style="line-height: 17.12px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><div><ul><li><b>Cyber Liability</b>&nbsp;– provides support and guidance if you’re hit by a cyber incident.&nbsp;</li><li><b>Legal Expenses&nbsp;</b>–&nbsp;protects your business in the event of legal action.&nbsp;</li><li><b>IR35 Protect&nbsp;</b>–&nbsp;safeguards your business from costs following an IR35 enquiry.&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div>I’ve attached some information about our add-ons in case you'd like to know more.<br><br>If you have any questions or wish to discuss these products in more detail, please give me a call on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br><span style="background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="background-color: white;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="background-color: white;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="background-color: white;">01242 808740</font></div></font></span></div>]]></td>
